name: Tsuji Gakuen Tsuji Cooking Kanshuu: Koharu no DS Uchigohan.: Shokuji Balance Guide Tsuki
overview: Tsuji Gakuen Tsuji Cooking Kanshuu - Koharu no DS Uchigohan. - Shokuji Balance Guide Tsuki is a Miscellaneous game, developed by OeRSTED and published by Comolink, which was released in Japan in 2007.
